HEADWORD: Fearless
<hw>Fear"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Free from fear.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Bold; daring; courageous; intrepid; valorous;
valiant; brave; undaunted; dauntless; heroic.</syn></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Fear"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Fear"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fearnaught</ent>⟦br⟧
